## High-Level Architecture

```
[User Browser]
      │
      ▼
[Next.js App — Vercel]
      │
      ├── /app           → Page routes (App Router)
      ├── /components    → UI components
      ├── /lib           → Data utils, types, mock data
      └── /public/dataset → Cleaned dataset (public download)
            │
            ▼
      [Data Layer]
      ├── Mock data (prototype)     → lib/mock-data.ts
      ├── CSV upload (papaparse)    → client-side parsing
      └── Live API (future)         → annotated integration points
```

---

## Directory Structure

```
my-app/
├── app/
│   ├── layout.tsx          — root layout, fonts, global providers
│   ├── page.tsx            — main entry point / home screen
│   ├── [feature]/
│   │   └── page.tsx        — feature-specific routes
│   └── globals.css         — global styles, Tailwind base
├── components/
│   ├── ui/                 — shadcn/ui components (auto-generated, do not edit)
│   └── [feature]/          — feature-specific components
├── lib/
│   ├── mock-data.ts        — representative sample data (matches DATA_MODEL.md schema)
│   ├── data-utils.ts       — wrangling helpers: filter, aggregate, normalize
│   └── types.ts            — TypeScript interfaces for all data models
├── public/
│   └── dataset/            — cleaned dataset files for public download
│       └── README.md       — field glossary, sources, license
├── package.json
└── README.md               — setup + research context
```

