## Data Flow

```
[Raw data source]
      │  acquisition script / manual download
      ▼
[Raw data]  →  lib/data-utils.ts  →  [Cleaned data]  →  lib/mock-data.ts (prototype)
                                                      →  public/dataset/  (published)
                                                      →  React state      (runtime)
```

